=Marry Me Again=

2
00:00:53,020 --> 00:00:55,940
=Episode 14=

3
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:09,920
Why are you here?

4
00:01:14,910 --> 00:01:16,640
- Hi.
- Didn't you promise no drinks?

5
00:01:18,510 --> 00:01:19,920
I said only when you were around,

6
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,070
I wouldn't drink.

7
00:01:21,070 --> 00:01:22,560
You plan to drink alone with him?

8
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,120
No way.

9
00:01:26,650 --> 00:01:27,680
Why did you do this to me?

10
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,600
Why?

11
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,230
You're asking me why?

12
00:01:30,430 --> 00:01:31,760
How can you drink alone with a grown man

13
00:01:31,790 --> 00:01:33,590
in a hotel room?

14
00:01:33,590 --> 00:01:35,430
Wasn't I alone with you,

15
00:01:35,430 --> 00:01:36,790
a grown man, in a room yesterday?

16
00:01:47,820 --> 00:01:49,150
You ordered quite a lot of drinks.

17
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,120
Can't finish them? Count me in.

18
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:55,840
This is ridiculous.

19
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,440
The rule still stands.

20
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,270
No drinking for you.

21
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:27,390
Let's play a game.

22
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:29,080
Sure, what game?

23
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,600
"I have,

24
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,040
you don't."

25
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:35,950
So cliche.

26
00:02:36,310 --> 00:02:37,230
So cliche?

27
00:02:37,870 --> 00:02:39,710
Uncle, are you scared to play?

28
00:02:40,310 --> 00:02:41,680
Uncle is, after all, the elder.

29
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,990
It's fine if he doesn't know how.

30
00:02:45,350 --> 00:02:46,520
You two keep calling me Uncle,

31
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,670
are you teasing me?

32
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,150
You're overthinking.

33
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:50,310
Uncle, it's fine if you don't.

34
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,990
Huaijin and I can still play.

35
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,680
Let's stick to the usual rules.

36
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,990
Whoever folds all five fingers first
gets to drink.

37
00:02:57,630 --> 00:02:58,550
Alright.

38
00:02:58,910 --> 00:02:59,990
Who said I was scared?

39
00:03:00,310 --> 00:03:01,230
Uncle,

40
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,830
don't force yourself.

41
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:04,920
Games like this can expose secrets,

42
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,710
especially for someone
with a lot to hide.

43
00:03:08,870 --> 00:03:09,790
Let's start.

44
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,200
What are we waiting for?

45
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,670
I'll go first.

46
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:22,160
I once drank 15 bottles
of beer in one go.

47
00:03:24,150 --> 00:03:25,280
Seriously?

48
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,870
I drown my sorrows alone,

49
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:28,320
but why did you two drink so much?

50
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,600
You're proud of being an alcoholic?

51
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:32,350
My turn.

52
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:34,560
I once liked a girl

53
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,670
for over five years.

54
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:45,200
I once shared a bed with Hua Ruoyi.

55
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,150
Huaijin,

56
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:49,390
when did we...?

57
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:50,520
You forgot?

58
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,430
The last time I was sick,
you took care of me.

59
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:53,400
You were so tired

60
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,950
that you fell asleep on my shoulder.

61
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,390
Does that count too?

62
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,800
By your logic,

63
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,520
I share a bed with myself every night.

64
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,760
Does that count too?

65
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,040
My turn.

66
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:05,310
I once ate a love bento

67
00:04:05,310 --> 00:04:07,560
made especially for me by Mi Chuxia.

68
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,910
Hua Ruoyi once drooled on my suit.

69
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:10,910
Let's skip that part.

70
00:04:10,910 --> 00:04:13,950
I once carried a drunken Mi Chuxia home.

71
00:04:14,150 --> 00:04:15,710
That was an accident, Huaijin.

72
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:16,680
And we even...

73
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,680
Stop talking.

74
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:19,080
Even...

75
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,560
What else did you do?

76
00:04:34,510 --> 00:04:35,430
Nothing.

77
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,680
I think this game is getting boring.

78
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,760
Let's switch.

79
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,200
Okay, switch it up.

80
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,920
Uncle, come on.

81
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:10,590
What's up with you?

82
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:12,000
Mu Huaijin carried you home too.

83
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,180
What happened between you two?

84
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:14,790
We...

85
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,350
None of your business.

86
00:05:18,030 --> 00:05:18,980
Hua Ruoyi,

87
00:05:18,980 --> 00:05:19,870
no one knows better than me

88
00:05:19,870 --> 00:05:21,270
how unruly you get when drunk.

89
00:05:21,630 --> 00:05:22,510
Tell me,

90
00:05:22,510 --> 00:05:23,680
did you treat him like you treat me?

91
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:25,030
Lu Nianbai,

92
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:27,360
there's nothing
between me and Mu Huaijin.

93
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,590
And there never will be.

94
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,720
Besides, you're

95
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,710
so focused on us two.

96
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,270
Why?

97
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:33,200
Jealous?

98
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:34,800
Yes, I'm jealous.

99
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:42,710
Hua Ruoyi, listen up.

100
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:55,310
You're mine.

101
00:05:59,130 --> 00:06:01,770
♪No time to say goodbye♪

102
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,160
Lu Nianbai.

103
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,350
Lu Nianbai!

104
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,120
Are you insane?

105
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,480
Let go.

106
00:06:14,890 --> 00:06:20,220
♪Don't say you're sorry, it's too cruel♪

107
00:06:22,670 --> 00:06:28,050
♪So much left unspoken, all forgiven♪

108
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:34,640
♪Singing softly, echoes lingering♪

109
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:38,460
♪All the stubbornness I regret♪

110
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:42,500
♪Can't forget, you were my sun♪

111
00:06:42,850 --> 00:06:46,430
♪Yet I feared the light you shone♪

112
00:06:46,670 --> 00:06:50,240
♪Singing lightly, tinged with sorrow♪

113
00:06:50,650 --> 00:06:54,140
♪I return to every place we knew♪

114
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:58,270
♪My growth, your reflection♪

115
00:06:59,250 --> 00:07:02,790
