124
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,360
Don't want to be responsible?

125
00:08:19,310 --> 00:08:21,030
Shouldn't you be responsible?

126
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,120
Alright, forget it.

127
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,880
