132
00:08:35,910 --> 00:08:37,040
Go, quick!

133
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,230
Hurry, get moving.

134
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,270
Go...

135
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:42,680
