147
00:08:59,670 --> 00:09:00,920
Let's discuss.

148
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,680
Sure, I'll be right there.

149
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:04,800
Please...

150
00:09:15,390 --> 00:09:17,560
